meta_description: JobContax is a recruitment agency that specialises in the Engineering - Design | Construction - Infrastructure | Life Sciences | Manufacturing - Food & Beverage sectors in Australia
paragraph:
JobContax has operated in the Australian market since 2001.
In Australia, JobContax specialises in the following sectors:

Engineering - Design
Construction - Infrastructure
Life Sciences
Manufacturing
Food & Beverage

JobContax recruits for EPCm Consultancies and contractors including Amec, Amgen, BHP Billiton, Carillion, Coca Cola, Emaar, GSK, Habtoor Leighton, Intel, Jacobs Engineering, J&J, Pfizer, Saint Gobain, Shell and many more.
